{
  "stem": "21349.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And like the Nazis wanted, the less you know, the more you could impress them with their philosophy and they would believe everything, you see.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He didn't have a mind of its own.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That came in different way.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As I mentioned before, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] after Kristallnacht, we wrote to all these friends again, all over.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And now it became actually serious, dangerous to stay in Germany.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So when this cousin of my father's who was living in Saskatchewan-- Yorkton, Saskatchewan, and he was a farmer.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And since in-- in Canada they have a parliament-- at that time they had a parliament.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they have congresspeople they call an MP, Member of Parliament, MO.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They had a member of parliament.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And in these small places like he was, he was very close to this friend.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And this friend, you see, was able that they made a special law for us to come in.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They sent us then what we called a landing card.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We are allowed to land in Canada.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] However, even with the landing card, it wasn't easy, because now we had to have money to go by boat.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] The Germans wanted at that time that all the Jewish people should leave the money in Germany as much as possible.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And not only this.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "If they would travel outside, they should lose-- use a German shipping company-- there were two Germany shipping companies-- and not [NON-ENGLISH] from Hamburg.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "My father went there and they told him, we have no vacancy, no place 'til two years from now.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we didn't want to wait two years, of course, because things were getting worse every day.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So he went to Hamburg.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Hamburg was the biggest city.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
